snippet.title: Alvin Roe
snippet.description:
Hi and welcome to my channel! 

My dream is to create a channel that spreads the joy of creating games. I'm still learning what that means. Tutorials. Devlogs. Motivation. I have no idea! All I know is that I am grateful to those who passed this torch to me, and I would love to pass it to you as well.

I have an irrational fear of death which makes me time conscious. I don't think I would have this anxiety, if I wasn't so grateful to be alive. I love that you spend your time with me, and I'm so thankful that you do. Video games are part of the reason I love life so much, and I want to bring that joy to others, whether its from a game I make, or teaching others the same joy of creating them. 

Thank you so much! If you want to know anything else, send me a message or leave a comment! 

Have the best day!
